text: ZY, Z.Y., or Zy may refer to: * ZY, a women's clothing chain by WE (clothing) * ZY, a model of Mazda Z engine * Sky Airlines (IATA code ZY) * Zy.com, a company formed by ZyWeb * ZY 1, also called CBERS-1, a satellite launched via the China–Brazil Earth Resources Satellite program * 2ZY, a radio station broadcast by BBC from Manchester, England in the 1920s * ZY, assistant (with ZL and ZR) of Golden Age superhero Masked Marvel (Centaur Publications)
title: ZY
